    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat</b> The ogre boss closes with soft-looking enemies and uses her massive reach (with Lunge, if necessary) to box them in."
        },
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> temperate or cold hills"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Violence is a way of life for ogres. Most of them learn the best ways to cause pain from their clans\u2019 bosses, who mete out beatings for even the slightest infraction."
        }
    ],
